</li><li>Rivas Plata et al. (2012) A new classification for the family Graphidaceae (Ascomycota: Lecanoromycetes: Ostropales). Fungal Diversity 52: 107–121. <a href="http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs13225-011-0135-8" target="_blank">[Website]</a>
</li><li>Rivas Plata et al. (2008) When family matters: an analysis of Thelotremataceae (Lichenized Ascomycota: Ostropales) as bioindicators of ecological continuity in tropical forests. Biodiversity and Conservation 17: 1319–1351. <a href="http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs10531-007-9289-9" target="_blank">[Website]</a>
